Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 差不多来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 每日锻炼结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正要去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没和你来一局了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开店前的准备做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要继承家业的话 也是时候记得过来帮把手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说要继承家业了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.39,0:00:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有好多事情想要做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H大业？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 我有叫你来帮忙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你拿着吃饭的家伙做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是有两个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}昨夜7时左右 在涩谷区的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}发生了住在该区内的45岁的资产家遇袭事件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这种事情很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇袭的都是有钱人吧？ 和咱们家无关嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 如果你被卷入这类事件的话你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么办啊？ 被盯上的都是有钱人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了是「如果」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车到山前必有路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:01:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是老爸的话会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗？ 船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真像是有两个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要迟到？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 禁止骑摩托上学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次老师还训斥了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是骑去学校附近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算是回答吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他到底像谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说几次了 你拿着吃饭的家伙干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我最后一次看到老爸与妈妈的样子
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.99,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1500)\pos(696,365)\4a&Hff&}马车与公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.99,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1500)\pos(696,365)\blur1}马车与公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近两个月 我一直在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去一心先生那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他现在才自报身份出现在我面前？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生资产家遇袭事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会怎么办？ 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 只要有我阿尔弗雷德在就无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能松开缰绳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是上品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小林哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人问你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下 我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧？ 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么 手无寸铁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑简单的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家爷爷 那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 可能会有点粗暴 请进车内
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 赶快干掉那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 不能对你们客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 先要解决你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不了了 恶徒们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处决
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管家爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下死定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老头 你大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没能保护好大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿尔弗雷德已经没有活着的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就送你去另一个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要先清算这笔帐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对海瑟琳克家出手的罪孽之深 好好感受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂密的树叶成了缓冲垫 所以得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有个缓冲垫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「晚上好」的话有点太早了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿？ 为什么我会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你什么都不记得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走山路时的记忆我倒是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的 我叫夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特?海瑟琳克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要开这种玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小林哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特?海瑟…琳克？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像公主的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为我就是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要开这种玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我没意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种事情不是很习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于摸入睡女孩的胸部却习以为常？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧 对 偶然间碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我相信哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是都记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是和胸部事件扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂什么扯平了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 男生果然都喜欢大胸部的女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 因人而异…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩托车坏掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 没想像中的严重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和陌生男人在一起的话 会被训斥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那还真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来马车还真有点那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 得回去取行李才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢让我有马一心等他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我女儿?佳苗的儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 是有马一心叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人我见多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背着的是刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话报警 有人违反刀枪管理法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我解释啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人是我重要的客人 不得怠慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一心老爷的客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 一心先生 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不叫我「外公」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时之间有点不适应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫「爷爷」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说老爸与妈妈不是意外身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到仇人之后你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就轮到别人来找你寻仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在这种仇恨与悲伤的无尽连锁中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳苗跟那个男人期望你过上这样的人生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的女儿死了难道你就不伤心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我还有你 我只剩下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…您的衣物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身打扮出席的话会失礼于各位来宾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在才问晚了点 你怎么会弄成这幅样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便救了下人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢 就这样出席吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了正确的事才弄脏衣物的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位对有马集团支持有加的董事以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…各位相关人员 抱歉让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫有马哲平 我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且也是有马集团总裁继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 继承人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必各位对于他这满身泥土的装束很是吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为他在来这里之前救了人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你救了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人叫夏洛特?海瑟琳克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是海瑟琳克的公主陛下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主…陛下？ 海瑟琳克公国？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的是公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位尽兴我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他这身装束对于他自己和各位来宾来说都有失礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请容他梳洗准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期间 请诸位畅谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总裁继承人是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了找到父母的仇人才来做你的养子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人会为你成为继承人一事而感到不悦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让对方明白这点 我才故意上演了刚才那幕闹剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗 佳苗是正统继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正统继承人？ 所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方不会马上露出马脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先要结交同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你要跟靠近你的人搞好关系 不管是不是刚才宴会上的那群小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平君跟您父亲还真是像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我也问候一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有马钢厂专务 敝姓外村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人当中…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多成年人可不应该「围观」一个孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他也感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范?霍森卿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍森卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位想做有马先生的公子的护卫 不如去申请特别许可如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然范?霍森卿这么吩咐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都拚命想通过你来巴结一心先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫文森特?范?霍森
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给介绍一下我的女儿们吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 这个哥哥就是爷爷的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能叫爷爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 她还不懂礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我叫玛利亚?范?霍森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫有马哲平 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你很拘谨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尔维呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不知去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 真拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 哲平君 今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心先生一登场 会场气氛都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好厉害的领袖气质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你的身上我也感受到了相同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差不多也适应会场气氛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平先生 您方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪笑脸就累得我精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起你就对我很关照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女仆呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆 真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看我像什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 的确除了女仆什么都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,货真价实的女仆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平先生 您要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种让人搞不清状况的时候 活动身体是最有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想和西洋剑切磋一下试试
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真般配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,般配？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个哥哥和姐姐一样厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他哥哥还早了点 玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了不少事呢 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们通过剑彼此了解了对方吧？ 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是西尔维娅?范?霍森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚妻？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平的父亲随身带着像棒子一样的怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟是做什么职业的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案是：荞麦面师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集公主恋人 学园与再会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Japanese food吗 真棒


